00:00:42.590 --> 00:00:47.430
for her outstanding
support and the volunteers

00:00:47.430 --> 00:00:50.450
who make this book
festival possible.

00:00:50.450 --> 00:00:55.560
This book is very special
and has touched our hearts.

00:00:55.560 --> 00:00:59.350
This tells about the
ultimate value of life.

00:00:59.350 --> 00:01:04.670
And how Dr. Roberto
Canessa fight for survival

00:01:04.670 --> 00:01:11.690
in the Andes had made him a fighter
for his most precious patients,

00:01:11.690 --> 00:01:17.290
his unborn and newborn
infant with congenital

00:01:17.290 --> 00:01:21.910
and life threatening heart
conditions and the struggle

00:01:21.910 --> 00:01:28.270
to save those precious lives and
to accompany them through time.

00:01:28.270 --> 00:01:33.570
It also reveal how the cooperation
between doctors around the world

00:01:33.570 --> 00:01:39.180
and hospitals in the United
States and in Uruguay organize

00:01:39.180 --> 00:01:44.360
to save them, fighting
against all odds.

00:01:44.360 --> 00:01:49.260
I forgot how many times
I have bought this book

00:01:49.260 --> 00:01:51.490
since its publication last March.

00:01:51.490 --> 00:01:56.840 position:56%
First, I bought it for myself, but
then also for friends and to members

00:01:56.840 --> 00:02:02.360
of the press and to teachers
who wanted to share this story

00:02:02.360 --> 00:02:07.700
with their students,
which is without doubt,

00:02:07.700 --> 00:02:12.910
our one of the most
incredible in human history.

00:02:12.910 --> 00:02:19.730
Later on, with my friends' feedback
and story of sleepless nights

00:02:19.730 --> 00:02:25.070
and sorrowful crying, I
realized that my relationship

00:02:25.070 --> 00:02:31.590
with my friends grew stronger and
that thanks to this wonderful book,

00:02:31.590 --> 00:02:36.870 position:56%
my friends got to know the
Uruguayan spirit, of always fighting

00:02:36.870 --> 00:02:44.340
to the end, of never giving
up, of solidarity and humanism,

00:02:44.340 --> 00:02:48.710
that can be seen in our soccer,
but also in the dedication

00:02:48.710 --> 00:02:54.530
of our UN peacekeepers, and
our commitment in the defense

00:02:54.530 --> 00:02:58.480
and promotion of human
rights and democracy.

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:05.570
This book has become my dearest
friend and my favorite gift.

00:03:05.570 --> 00:03:11.510
I hope it would become the gift
you can give to your family members

00:03:11.510 --> 00:03:15.930
and your friends, and
share this moving story.

00:03:15.930 --> 00:03:20.730
I feel it can help to
enliven our communities,

00:03:20.730 --> 00:03:24.240
promoting mutual help
and social harmony.

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:26.040
