They say something but
they act in some way else.

00:27:13.850 --> 00:27:15.840
&gt;&gt; Ted Robbins: You're
talking about politician?

00:27:15.840 --> 00:27:17.710
&gt;&gt; Roberto Canessa: No,
no I'm talking about--

00:27:17.710 --> 00:27:21.510
politicians are the
reflection of the voters.

