00:28:53.020 --> 00:28:54.690
and common moments in your life.

00:28:54.690 --> 00:28:57.760
Would you share some of those?

00:28:57.760 --> 00:28:59.060
&gt;&gt; Roberto Canessa: Yes.

00:28:59.060 --> 00:29:03.140
I think there's like a
titanium and steel link

00:29:03.140 --> 00:29:04.590
with the patients, you know.

00:29:04.590 --> 00:29:08.360
And a family you never saw
in your life and comes to you

00:29:08.360 --> 00:29:11.950
with a purest thing that
