they would say I don't
want your face in your book

00:29:44.510 --> 00:29:48.110
and then their kids which is 12
years old, there's the mother,

00:29:48.110 --> 00:29:50.370
how couldn't I be in
Roberto's book, mommy.

00:29:50.370 --> 00:29:51.980
He saved my life.

