The doctor was saying we
must cross our fingers.

00:30:20.040 --> 00:30:22.920
And the mother was calling me, we
didn't come to cross the fingers,

00:30:22.920 --> 00:30:25.050
we come here to get the child cure.

00:30:25.050 --> 00:30:26.550
Well, I mean there are limits.

00:30:26.550 --> 00:30:28.900
Medicine is not magic.

00:30:28.900 --> 00:30:32.870
And then she comes around and
hugs me and it's delicious.

00:30:32.870 --> 00:30:34.170
It's great.

00:30:34.170 --> 00:30:35.820
I knew I was doing the right thing.

00:30:35.820 --> 00:30:38.500
&gt;&gt; Ted Robbins: You did the--
you interviewed the patients?

00:30:38.500 --> 00:30:39.800
&gt;&gt; Roberto Canessa: No, not at all.

00:30:39.800 --> 00:30:41.100
Pablo didn't allow me, he said,

00:30:41.100 --> 00:30:44.590
this is going to be very
sweet and very sticky.

00:30:44.590 --> 00:30:49.250
